    • Method Detail

      • verifyGraphsContainment

        default GC verifyGraphsContainment()
        Verifies this graph collection, removing dangling graph ids from its elements, i.e. ids not contained in the collection.
        This operator can be applied after an operator that has not checked the graphs validity. The graph head of this graph collection remains unchanged.
        Returns:
        this graph collection with all dangling graph ids removed.
